[node name="PAGINA" parent="." unique_id=1772091157 instance=ExtResource("110_pn")]
position = Vector2(1450, 1241)
text = "[i]Found pinned to a crooked branch.[/i]

The woods forget their own name here. The paths lie — the widest, easiest ones only circle back on themselves.

Follow the fireflies, not the roads; they keep the way the forest lost.

And if you meet her — the woman who fades — say her name aloud. A name is the last thread the Void cannot unspool."

